flowchart TD
  U[User request] --> P[Planner LLM
  - sees tool list
  - outputs JSON plan only]
  P -->|plan JSON| V[Trust Boundary / Validator
  - parse JSON
  - schema validation
  - tool allowlist
  - arg constraints]
  V -->|validated call| E[Executor
  - maps tool name to function
  - executes deterministically
  - logs]
  E --> T[Tool / Service]
  T --> E
  E --> R[Final response]
  V -->|reject/repair| P
